{"tid":185042,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"召喚各位用左F牌德國洋甘菊花水有不尋常反應嘅巴絲","createTime":"2017-04-03T08:03:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-09T05:29:28.000Z","uid":21730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9b94581404c6bd0426fecb8e43cf9dc537ad3203","tid":185042,"uid":21730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T08:03:54.000Z","msg":"事源：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ahyauyau/posts/10158529349705626\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fahyauyau%2Fposts%2F10158529349705626&d=m5XrLHEHhhS4xH%2BSicsBH49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=448a4126\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ahyauyau/posts/10158529349705626</a><br />\n<br />\nEros 回應：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/florihanaeroshk/posts/1275802955849634\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fflorihanaeroshk%2Fposts%2F1275802955849634&d=m5XrLHEHhhS4xH%2BSicsBH49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=aee6bbc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/florihanaeroshk/posts/1275802955849634</a><br />\n<br />\n我自己都有買過呢批，隻味的確係比以前刺鼻好多，我自己都覺得批次有問題<br />\n但係事主個fb 俾好多人插話佢自己敏感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想睇下有幾多巴絲出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39b4c914a1a2b40f6fd9a3f1dd8a9130e80f177c","tid":185042,"uid":71694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T08:06:34.000Z","msg":"我用完對奶好敏感"},{"pid":"4d5f49eed496dc0f262fdde97cf3269c3e600d03","tid":185042,"uid":20302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T08:08:31.000Z","msg":"用過三枝 <br />\n乜事都冇<br />\n<br />\n講真 敏感呢家野 用各大護膚品都有機會架啦"},{"pid":"8be89586d8d8c062d9d1e9110f29bd41c56a3bb4","tid":185042,"uid":18564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T08:15:04.000Z","msg":"怕敏感點解唔試左用羅甘先...."},{"pid":"ad05bcdb34c20402ad2d2d5419a8e4dcc4e1c7ed","tid":185042,"uid":21730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T08:17:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>怕敏感點解唔試左用羅甘先....</blockquote><br />\n其實事主係用開德甘喎 點解要用羅甘先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0a70ef8ddee05ed9b127f21427f841f9c92beaa","tid":185042,"uid":21730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T08:18:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用過三枝 <br />\n乜事都冇<br />\n<br />\n講真 敏感呢家野 用各大護膚品都有機會架啦</blockquote><br />\n我用過四枝 之前都一路無事 係呢啲特別古怪"},{"pid":"2ed0e2b94ae0cb0245386f273760bb82ac28fd4d","tid":185042,"uid":656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T04:46:44.000Z","msg":"我都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 刺鼻到一個點 本身明明係好香菊花茶味<br />\n邊係咁嘅味"},{"pid":"4f1279104a8047bf7ee8f18919d249036eb46ac6","tid":185042,"uid":53652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T04:53:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96ad22e23c6c939b161a6c98f1ccb551a1885a2f","tid":185042,"uid":54965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T05:43:05.000Z","msg":"我唔係用洋甘菊 但之前用永久花濕敷又紅又拿到流眼水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14c93adf53b5a2b7f9f49b8a90160b2d81dd4a19","tid":185042,"uid":53166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T07:41:26.000Z","msg":"我10月響EROS買左FLH015-250726F批次既德國洋甘菊花水<br />\n之前響其他post都報告過幾次用完3秒對眼同塊面已經勁lar<br />\nptt見過台灣絲打都有呢個問題, 話係精油濃度高, 試過溝其他花水/水都完全冇用<br />\n前日先再拎出黎再用都重係lar, 不過冇之前lar得咁勁"},{"pid":"2daba896d9e99bba82c916f49f527c7ce7fc2887","tid":185042,"uid":53166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T07:43:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用過三枝 <br />\n乜事都冇<br />\n<br />\n講真 敏感呢家野 用各大護膚品都有機會架啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔關事, 我去另1間買左支100ML德甘試過完全冇事,<br />\n之後去EROS買左支500ML有問題批次先出事"},{"pid":"2aa6617a4080d1197c3b0c4e708ac2c36e1901b8","tid":185042,"uid":53166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T07:53:18.000Z","msg":"俾番LINK大家參考番<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Aromatherapy/M.1473344709.A.038.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FAromatherapy%2FM.1473344709.A.038.html&d=m5XrLHEHhhS4xH%2BSicsBH49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=e74b7fb8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Aromatherapy/M.1473344709.A.038.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Aromatherapy/M.1476105650.A.ADC.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FAromatherapy%2FM.1476105650.A.ADC.html&d=m5XrLHEHhhS4xH%2BSicsBH49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=ca5c166e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Aromatherapy/M.1476105650.A.ADC.html</a>"},{"pid":"1e4c7539a11e4abfdec5d520206d32a98819264d","tid":185042,"uid":85578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T11:45:13.000Z","msg":"我都係受害者之一<br />\n<br />\n果陣第一次用，拎黎濕敷，過左幾分塊面已經開始有灼熱既感覺，跟住直情係&quot;拿&quot;面，超痛，<br />\n<br />\n第二、三唔信邪再用，都係過幾次就拿面同埋好痛，嚇到唔敢再用"},{"pid":"edad7d66b07a6c3e7bac9b89ffce6444f93f68e7","tid":185042,"uid":6767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T17:10:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上年10月尾買過德甘 又係拿到紅晒<br />\n明明之前用都無問題"},{"pid":"3af917eda2e4bfd98fd39207b32df097bc764250","tid":185042,"uid":656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:17:51.000Z","msg":"好多受害者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁多人唔係個別事件啦掛"},{"pid":"46f6f7a6ac02c42038c8c30f5308078eb129bbe2","tid":185042,"uid":42318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:42:20.000Z","msg":"其中一個 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乸到眼水都標埋"},{"pid":"989d1ad3040bbd91720e0e43cdeff70c3f2280ad","tid":185042,"uid":656,"like":0,"disli